text:
RT @cliffordlevy: Scoop: Jared and Ivanka are spurning NYC and expanding in NJ. Their “cottage” on the grounds of the Trump National Golf Club is getting a relocated heliport, and a spa and yoga complex.
By @NYTLiz

name: nytimes
text:
Dave Chappelle said it may have been legal for ViacomCBS to license “Chappelle’s Show” to Netflix and HBOMax without paying him or even informing him, “because I signed the contract.”

“But is that right?” he said. “I didn’t think so either.” https://t.co/IHDDRfyJQZ
